text:
Juri, what's wrong? You suddenly stopped.
If you're tired, I can help carry your bags.
Nah, it's not that I'm tired. It's just that, you know...
Thinking that today's the last day here...

Even though it was only a few days,
I feel like I've become a student here.
That just shows how fulfilling this training camp was.
I want to come back here again.
Anyway, let's hurry up and tidy things up.

Until everything's finished, it's still part of the camp,
so we can't neglect stuff like this!
